8 03:30:00', 'none', '7', '4', '1'), ('63', 'Crazy Puppet\'s', '2012-09-07 23:00:00', null, '7', '4', '1'), ('64', 'The Dirty Papy', '2012-09-08 03:30:00', 'none', '7', '4', '1'), ('66', 'Chukks', '2012-09-06 23:00:00', null, '7', '2', '1'), ('67', 'RiotBoy', '2012-09-08 02:30:00', 'none', '7', '4', '1'), ('68', 'Tr3lux', '2012-09-08 00:00:00', 'none', '7', '4', '1'), ('69', 'Dim', '2012-09-07 23:30:00', null, '7', '6', '1'), ('70', 'La Vie C\'est Facile', '2012-09-06 17:00:00', null, '7', '7', '1'), ('71', 'Radiorifle', '2012-09-08 19:00:00', null, '7', '7', '1'), ('72', 'Pascal Viscardi', '2012-09-07 17:00:00', null, '7', '1', '1'), ('73', 'Ngoc Lan', '2012-09-08 23:00:00', null, '7', '4', '1'), ('74', 'Koma Dub', '2012-09-09 00:00:00', 'none', '7', '3', '1'), ('75', 'Supermafia Vj\'s', '2012-09-06 17:00:00', null, '7', '1', '1'), ('76', 'Supermafia Vj\'s', '2012-09-07 17:00:00', null, '7', '1', '1'), ('77', 'Supermafia Vj\'s', '2012-09-08 17:00:00', null, '7', '1', '1'), ('79', 'Conférence et démonstration : le son multicanal en 3D - L\'immersion sonore', '2012-09-07 17:00:00', 'Dr. Christof Faller, lecturer at the audio-visual communications laboratory of the EPFL and the director of Illusonic, will bring forward the various ways to present the sound in order to achieve maximum sound quality leading to better appreciation when listenig to music.', '7', '8', '4'), ('80', 'Workshop : initiation à la production musicale', '2012-09-07 15:00:00', 'A workshop offering an introduction to various production techniques enabling you to compose music with the help of your computer and to combine different tools as well as digital instruments.', '7', '8', '4'), ('81', 'La culture D.I.Y, l\'open source et le copyright', '2012-09-07 18:00:00', 'Access to means of creation and information has rather evolved since the advent of the internet and the computer in the majority of households the past ten years. If this assessment can be pleasing because of its enormous creative and networking potential, it can also be frightening in terms of control and the consequences it can have on the artist who wishes to live on it: illegal downloading, copyright. What are the consequences of these changes in the creation and consumption process among visual and musical cultures ? Does free culture have limits, ethical codes to respect ? Does this extreme accessibility have an impact on the quality of the creation ?\r\n\r\nGuests:\r\nDomenico Quaranta, Art critic and Curator\r\nLemonade, Band\r\nLéo Wannaz, Owner of the music label Creaked\r\n\r\nModerator:\r\nYan Luong\r\n\r\n', '7', '8', '3'), ('82', 'Initiation au mix + Showcase Numark', '2012-09-08 11:00:00', 'An introduction to mix will enable participants of all ages to discover how to use DJ equipment as well as the various techniques peculiar to DJing. DJ Volta, DJ and experienced producer, will demonstrate the power of today’s Numark branded controllers and will treat you to his personal mix !', '7', '8', '4'), ('83', 'Showcase Feeltune', '2012-09-08 13:00:00', 'The Feeltune team will be represented by Nicolas Piau, Feeltune’s boss, Rhizome inventor and experienced DJ, as well as Bryce Warner, Feeltune sales manager for Europe and Asia. They will present and propose interactive tests and demonstrations on the SXE Rhizome and the LE Rhizome.', '7', '8', '4'), ('84', 'Conférence et Showcase Theremin (proposé par le NODE)', '2012-09-08 14:00:00', 'The CArTe is inviting the NODE in order to share the passion and knowledge peculiar to the Theremin instrument. A conference given by Coralie Ehinger, NODE’s founder and co-director, will be followed by a performance given by Jimmy Virani, french thereminist, who’s Hawaiian and exotic sounds will allow us to extend summer’s warmth so as to ease the shift to autumn.', '7', '8', '4'), ('85', 'Showcase Ableton with special guest Jeremy P. Caulfield', '2012-09-08 15:00:00', 'The artist Jeremy P. Caulfield from the famous german label Vakant will demonstrate the infinite possibilities the Ableton LIVE software can offer to any composer or DJ. He will give you tips and show you how to work with the live software for djing, studio production and naturally for the on-stage “live”.', '7', '8', '4'), ('86', 'Showcase Arturia with JOAKIM (Tigersushi, Versatile - FR)', '2012-09-08 16:00:00', 'Présentation du MiniBrute, le premier synthétiseur purement analogique, ainsi que de SPARK, la boîte à rythme «Hybrid» de la marque française Arturia. Joakim (Tigersushi, Versatile - FR) vous surprendra avec ses deux produits qu’il utilise personnellement pour ses propres productions !', '7', '8', '4'), ('87', 'Session libre', '2012-09-08 17:00:00', 'An open session where the public will have the opportunity to freely test the various instruments and software as much as ask the reps and specialists for each of the presented brands for information.', '7', '8', '4'), ('88', 'Workshop et conférence Numark', '2012-09-09 13:00:00', 'DJ Volta is an experienced international DJ and producer who owns his own djing and musical production school. He will demonstrate in particular the power of the new Numark “4Trak” controller. Lionel Singh, representative of various brands (Numark, Ableton, Arturia), will explain to you the advantages of this new incredible controller devoted to Native Instrument’s software named “Traktor”.', '7', '8', '4'), ('89', 'Workshop et conférence Arturia', '2012-09-09 14:00:00', 'Arturia’s products are music instruments used by famous artists and producers all over the world such as Jean-Michel Jarre, Herbie Hancock, DeadMau5, Trent Reznor, Air, Phoenix and many more. Romain Dejoie, french brand Arturia’s specialist, will primarily present to you the MiniBrute in details as well as the hybrid SPARK controller devoted to the big sounds of legendary rhythm boxes. MiniBrute is a purely analogue synthesizer which has already received many famous awards !', '7', '8', '4'), ('90', 'Showcase Akai', '2012-09-09 15:00:00', 'In charge of the MPC demonstrations for Akai Professional all over Europe and music producer at BMG Publishing, Andy Mak will make a demonstration of the new Akai MPC Renaissance controller and of the software. A showcase-workshop allowing the discovery of the wide range of production techniques offered by the Akai machines ; from sampling to beat making and the integration of a virtual instrument, to name just a few !', '7', '8', '4'), ('91', 'Workshop et conférence Ableton', '2012-09-09 16:00:00', 'Konpiuta, a musician with an incredible musical career, will introduce you to his personal vision of Ableton LIVE. His frequent invitations to play beyond our borders challenges established thinking, according to which swiss music is not highly marketable outside of Switzerland. Regarding the slap in your face you will get when seeing his live show, it will certainly make you think twice about the saying “no man is a prophet in his own country” !', '7', '8', '4'), ('92', 'Workshop et conférence Feeltune', '2012-09-09 17:00:00', 'Nicolas Piau and Bryce Warner will be presenting the SXE Rhizome in stand-alone, the LE Rhizome with a Mac and, exclusively for the Electrosanne festival and as a world premiere, the last-born of the Feeltune product line !', '7', '8', '4'), ('93', 'Musique et arts visuels : l\'outil internet comme moyen de diffusion', '2012-09-08 18:00:00', 'En parallèle avec le thème de l’exposition «L’aura de l’œuvre d’art soumis aux enjeux des nouvelles technologies et d’internet», nous proposons une discussion autour de l’utilisation de ce moyen de diffusion de masse. Dans quelle mesure internet peut-il nous servir à diffuser des propos, des images, de la musique ? Blog, webzines, réseaux sociaux, quelles sont les différentes plateformes existantes pour se promouvoir et comment s’en faire connaître ? Est-il encore possible à l’heure actuelle d’en faire fi ?\r\n\r\nInvités:\r\nSouleiman Bouri, Phonograph corp, webzine musical\r\nStéphane Devidal, artiste\r\nThomas Koenig, artiste\r\nRound Table Knights, producteurs et DJ\'s\r\nSophie Yerly, créatrice du blog www.we-find-wildness.com\r\n\r\nModérateur:\r\nYan Luong\r\n\r\n', '7', '8', '3'), ('96', 'Gregorythme (live)', '2012-09-08 22:30:00', '', '7', '1', '1'), ('100', 'Live - Production Salon', '2013-05-24 09:47:00', 'live show', '8', '1', '2');
COMMIT;

